Help Type: command
Command: spinedigest sdpub info

sdpub info

Purpose:
  Print archive metadata and high-level summary counts.

Usage:
  spinedigest sdpub info --input <path> [--help|-h]

Output shape:
  - Title
  - Authors
  - Language
  - Source Format
  - Identifier
  - Publisher
  - Published At
  - Description
  - Cover presence and cover metadata
  - Top-level section count
  - Referenced serial count
  - Total fragment count

Notes:
  - Missing metadata fields are omitted.
  - If no document metadata exists, the command prints a fallback message.
